{"tid":2252644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話你知國泰今次炒人，唯一值得恥笑嘅係咩","createTime":"2020-10-21T15:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T16:52:16.000Z","uid":70915,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e8298de10d4eb87d87a66578e44e262d37abc3c6","tid":2252644,"uid":70915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T15:07:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">就係班篤灰藍絲撚屌、水炮車都照炒</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為篤灰就有位上？藍絲就有人保？<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">吔屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乞食啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">希望大家勿忘初心</span><br />\n<br />\n今次炒人其實係勞工市場史上最大災難<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">但罪魁禍首係邊個？<br />\n係武漢肺炎、係垃圾中共同林鄭政府呀<br />\n唔撚封關呀！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">點解個個唔覺得憤怒？而係心涼、恥笑？</span><br />\n<br />\n有無諗過下個可能係<br />\n你自己、你公司、你果行？<br />\n<br />\n大家都係打工仔、受害者，唔企同一陣線<br />\n反而走去落井下石？<br />\n<br />\n有無諗過，你不負責任嘅恥笑言論<br />\n正正幫左呢個垃圾政府<br />\n完美spin走輿論焦點，加速分化？？<br />\n<br />\n航空手足付出幾多，無需多講<br />\n只要記住：<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">百業蕭條、大小規模炒人<br />\n全部都係垃圾政府責任！</span><br />\n<br />\n難怪香港勞工權益一直不能抬頭<br />\n工會無人參加<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">「睇人仆街最開心」嘅心態再唔改變<br />\n準備做一世大灣區狗奴才啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"38ea746c85c4d003e5a8857386a797f6c27067bf","tid":2252644,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T15:08:51.000Z","msg":"飛雞落地"},{"pid":"8024087844a4b06c8fadfaa1890b4aea8cc200c1","tid":2252644,"uid":70915,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"38ea746c85c4d003e5a8857386a797f6c27067bf","tid":2252644,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T15:08:51.000Z","msg":"飛雞落地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T15:11:09.000Z","msg":"自己衝入黎搏俾人block，on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝推po wo<img src=\"/assets/face